<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Premier League and European clubs are continuing to work hard to try and get transfer deals over the line with the new season now underway. </p>

<p>The clock is now beginning to tick and clubs have just a short period of time left to bring in any new faces.</p>

<p>The transfer window is open until October 5 - although a domestic-only one will stretch until October 16. There are sure to be plenty of twists and turns still to come, and you can follow all the latest news and gossip with Sportsmail.</p>

